.SS startproject
.INDENT 0.0
.IP \(bu 2
Syntax: \fBscrapy startproject <project_name>\fP
.IP \(bu 2
Requires project: \fIno\fP
.UNINDENT
.sp
Creates a new Scrapy project named \fBproject_name\fP, under the \fBproject_name\fP
directory.
.sp
Usage example:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
$ scrapy startproject myproject
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
